+sub_section( 'Setting Up Home and Blog Page' )

	ol
		li Navigate to #[+mark( 'nav', 'Appearance', 'Customize', 'Homepage Settings' )] (or you can also do this at #[+mark( 'nav', 'Settings', 'Reading' )]).
		li For "<strong>Your homepage displays</strong>" option set <em>"A static page"</em>.
		li Select your homepage and posts page from the dropdown lists. Posts page becomes your blog page.
